117
00:07:24,500 --> 00:07:26,200
For weight loss...

118
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:29,600
It's for a friend.

119
00:07:36,060 --> 00:07:37,813
How is her condition, Khun Tul?

120
00:07:37,813 --> 00:07:39,953
Could be asthma.

121
00:07:39,953 --> 00:07:42,620
Sira is searching for medicine right now. Just a second.

122
00:07:42,620 --> 00:07:45,387
