- Yes.

123
00:07:45,400 --> 00:07:47,700
Hurry, hurry, hurry!

124
00:07:52,553 --> 00:07:54,807
Let's try this one.

125
00:07:54,807 --> 00:07:56,167
Here.

126
00:07:57,100 --> 00:07:58,600
Khun Cream.

127
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:07,000
Are you feeling better?

128
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:11,200
Yes, I feel better now.

129
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:15,100
Thank you.

130
00:08:15,100 --> 00:08:17,400
Thanks.

131
00:08:17,400 --> 00:08:19,300
Thank you.

132
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:28,720
[Huern Hong Tor | Nan Coffee Shop]

133
00:08:34,500 --> 00:08:36,860
- Khun Cream.
- Oh, yes?

134
00:08:36,860 --> 00:08:39,800
Are you sure you're all right?

135
00:08:39,800 --> 00:08:42,800
If you want to rest, we can head back to the hotel.

136
00:08:42,800 --> 00:08:46,500
I'm okay. I really feel better, Khun Tul.

137
00:08:48,540 --> 00:08:50,307
Well...

138
00:08:51,300 --> 00:08:55,200
About your asthma... How long have you had it?

139
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:57,800
