140
00:08:58,500 --> 00:09:00,287
It's been a while.

141
00:09:00,300 --> 00:09:06,100
But it only flares up occasionally.

142
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:11,200
And the meds in your bag...

143
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,520
Khun Tul, why did you ask earlier

144
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:22,000
