145
00:09:28,700 --> 00:09:31,500
Pete sent me this picture.

146
00:09:35,300 --> 00:09:40,400
He said you two are getting back to how things used to be.

147
00:09:40,400 --> 00:09:42,400
And I saw you talking nicely with him

148
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:45,500
qo I thought you might be getting back together.

149
00:09:45,500 --> 00:09:47,200
That's not true, Khun Tul.

150
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:52,200
This photo it was taken right after I was attacked.

151
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:55,200
Attacked? Who attacked you?

152
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:58,800
Do you remember the day before we flew to Nan?

153
00:09:58,800 --> 00:10:01,500
When you called me and I hung up?

154
00:10:01,500 --> 00:10:04,300
That motorcycle that's been following me. He attacked me.

155
00:10:04,300 --> 00:10:05,900
Khun Pete happened to be there and helped me.

156
00:10:05,900 --> 00:10:09,200
Afterward, I passed out and he brought me to rest to the apartment.

157
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:12,000
Nothing else happened, for real, Khun Tul.

158
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:15,280
Khun Cream, if anything happens again,

159
00:10:15,280 --> 00:10:17,800
you have to tell me first.

160
00:10:19,100 --> 00:10:24,600
And I'm sorry I couldn't help you that night.

161
00:10:26,253 --> 00:10:30,980
As for Ai Pete, if you say it's nothing...

162
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:33,400
then it's nothing.

163
00:10:33,400 --> 00:10:35,300
I'll let it go.

164
00:10:40,133 --> 00:10:44,727
To be honest, Khun Pete and I...

165
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:50,200
We used to sort of date for a while.

166
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:52,600
But there's really nothing going on right now.

167
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:56,400
We're really just friends now, Khun Tul.

168
00:10:59,900 --> 00:11:04,300
Thank you, Khun Cream, for being honest with me.

169
00:11:06,100 --> 00:11:08,200
Really, thank you so much.

170
00:11:13,500 --> 00:11:18,800
And thank you and your team for your dedication.

171
00:11:18,800 --> 00:11:22,200
This project means a lot to me.

172
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:24,800
It's important to everyone too.

173
00:11:24,800 --> 00:11:29,000
I believe everyone at Dreamer wants to see the brand grow in its own direction,

174
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:33,200
