175
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:39,700
I'm really glad that I chose you.

176
00:11:40,400 --> 00:11:44,100
You've made everything better.

177
00:11:44,100 --> 00:11:50,100
Back when P'Ben was the boss, everyone was scared of him.

178
00:11:50,100 --> 00:11:51,520
