179
00:11:51,520 --> 00:11:54,700
It wasn't as relaxed as working with you.

180
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:59,800
Maybe because I'm close in age to the team so it's easier to talk.

181
00:11:59,800 --> 00:12:05,000
You've been smiling more too.

182
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:08,600
Really?

183
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:11,200
Yes.

184
00:12:11,200 --> 00:12:14,300
It's just that some of the team once told me

185
00:12:14,300 --> 00:12:17,900
you were like an ice prince.

186
00:12:19,700 --> 00:12:23,500
Then I'll give you the credit for thawing me out.

187
00:12:24,300 --> 00:12:27,000
I think it's not just the team that's more relaxed.

188
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:30,100
I am, too.

189
00:12:33,800 --> 00:12:35,600
It's strange.

190
00:12:38,900 --> 00:12:41,750
But when I'm with you,

191
00:12:41,750 --> 00:12:47,400
it feels like when I used to be with one of my close friends.

192
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:54,520
When I was with that person, I felt completely like myself.

193
00:12:55,100 --> 00:12:59,100
Fresh would be happy to hear that you still think of her.

194
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:06,000
How did you know I was talking about Fresh?

195
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:15,280
You talk about her all the time.

196
00:13:17,753 --> 00:13:22,680
Well, what I meant is...

197
00:13:24,280 --> 00:13:26,973
I talk about her as a friend.

198
00:13:26,973 --> 00:13:29,067
There's nothing more than that.

199
00:13:29,067 --> 00:13:30,547
Yes.

200
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:34,200
- Yes.
- Okay.

201
00:13:38,200 --> 00:13:40,000
[Wat Phumin (Temple), Wiang Tai Subdistrict, Zone 1, Mueang District, Nan Province]

202
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:43,200
Inside this chapel is the world-famous Whispering Love mural.

203
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:47,100
I want everyone to study the wall paintings and the artwork.

204
00:13:47,100 --> 00:13:49,200
You might get some ideas for your designs.

205
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:50,400
Got it, P'Cream.

206
00:13:50,400 --> 00:13:53,100
I'll take lots of pictures for the mood board too.

207
00:13:53,100 --> 00:13:54,500
Great.

208
00:13:55,800 --> 00:13:57,400
Let's go.

209
