00:17:13,533 --> 00:17:15,227
Cake.

254
00:17:15,227 --> 00:17:16,933
Cake.

255
00:17:18,773 --> 00:17:22,480
I'm sorry for startling you.

256
00:17:23,280 --> 00:17:26,140
